{"id": 1983, "genre": 1001, "title": "办了会员之后，你的花钱习惯都发生了啥变化？", "description": "最终是省了钱拿了实惠，还是花掉更多？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 896, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201710301741039X4T1LaP028M5Ofc.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-01T03:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 264708, "content": "办了卡，，除了又有一块儿塑料片儿占卡位以外没有任何用处。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 246791, "content": "就不爱办会员，因为并没有什么太多的卵用……为了计较那点福利还不如多赚点钱再", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542063}, {"id": 247818, "content": "哪有钱办会员……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181901}, {"id": 245771, "content": "只坐国航和深航，只为升金卡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891733}, {"id": 246557, "content": "花的钱更多，服务变的不那么好了只是程序化的表现服务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894603}, {"id": 246046, "content": "爱花钱也爱选性价比，被套路时候，争取自己想要的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040798}, {"id": 245792, "content": "看电影都看4d ，因为只有4d 场次有影城卡优惠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052526}, {"id": 245551, "content": "凑单送分", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712163}, {"id": 245552, "content": "每次都要被套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 195, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672038}, {"id": 245553, "content": "B站送了个大会员，emmm感觉也没啥感觉啊ヽ(`▭´)ﾉ✨", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058561}, {"id": 245554, "content": "京东plus...什么都在上面买，反正免运费??", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846056}, {"id": 245555, "content": "不办卡。快走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205852}, {"id": 245556, "content": "开了饿了么会员，以后只在饿了么点外卖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 52647}, {"id": 245557, "content": "开了饿了么会员，之后只在饿了么点外卖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 52647}, {"id": 245558, "content": "你们知道 不小心用touch id 付了年费QQ超级会员的痛吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788504}, {"id": 245562, "content": "在饿了么点餐，结算时说花十二办个会员本单可以减五元，果断点了不值。", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155485}, {"id": 245563, "content": "每月被自动扣的款变多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172715}, {"id": 245564, "content": "为了分，花了更多的钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719874}, {"id": 245566, "content": "远两公里也要去那家超市买东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970634}, {"id": 245568, "content": "写会员价的就想消费", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 245570, "content": "从不办会员，不值得", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159141}, {"id": 245571, "content": "只关注有会员账号的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953514}, {"id": 245574, "content": "没什么变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253159}, {"id": 245576, "content": "买东西前都习惯的说:我有会员卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145640}, {"id": 252233, "content": "办卡后买东西需要就买，有和没有一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200588}, {"id": 245578, "content": "办了之后不用", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1095135}, {"id": 245579, "content": "总是差一点就能凑够满减，等终于凑够满减了，冷静一想，其实都不是啥需要买的东西。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 245582, "content": "办了全家集享卡 推送消息多了 可都是刺激会员消费的 然而也没用多去买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800043}, {"id": 245584, "content": "会员要不就是有期限积分要不就是预付款甚至年费，反正总是希望借此机会能让你们不得不在我们这里消费用我们的服务，越依赖越上瘾越好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527010}, {"id": 245588, "content": "買會員的意義在於下次花錢更方便。多給自己一個花錢的理由。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 245845, "content": "为什么最近老提会员", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023664}, {"id": 245591, "content": "现实中多数时候能抵抗会员陷阱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 235507}, {"id": 245593, "content": "基本没变，该理性还是要理性。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673847}, {"id": 245595, "content": "关心最新优惠信息...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1220114}, {"id": 245597, "content": "办阅读会员之后读书多了点 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155587}, {"id": 245599, "content": "健身卡会员是好事吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070185}, {"id": 245601, "content": "PSN会员还是值得入的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221934}, {"id": 246625, "content": "从双十一可以看出，真应该剁手。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176113}, {"id": 245602, "content": "完全是被套路办了星巴克的会员卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597586}, {"id": 246370, "content": "更多花钱 尽量去这家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175145}, {"id": 246372, "content": "办卡和囤货基本差不多，容易习惯性浪费", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150156}, {"id": 246375, "content": "只在一家剪頭發、修甲、吃飯、買東西...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921750}, {"id": 246379, "content": "比之前花的更多，而且每次的卡最终也没有用完就不再去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478933}, {"id": 245616, "content": "凑单减免?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734793}, {"id": 245619, "content": "办了卡之后总想快点消费完，想着哪天店家倒闭了就没法用了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173111}, {"id": 245626, "content": "开了网易云音乐的会员，本来想听啥随便下。会员到期后，听歌都得加会员，只能续费...???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173138}, {"id": 245627, "content": "京东的plus，不再凑运费了，感觉消费降下来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637484}, {"id": 245628, "content": "应该是消费增加了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1172588}, {"id": 245630, "content": "没啥变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046553}, {"id": 245634, "content": "从不用会员 不喜欢被套牢的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 205291}]}